                              Use in Specific Populations (8.1)

                           ]. Advise females of reproductive potential to use effective contraception during treatment with FRINDOVYX and for up to 1 year after completion of therapy. Advise male patients with female partners of reproductive potential to use effective contraception during treatment with FRINDOVYX and for 4 months after completion of therapy [see Use in Specific Populations (8.1, 8.3)].

